# Supabase invariants

## Tables / columns

- `doc_chunks.embedding` must remain `vector(1024)` (BGE-M3).
- `knowledge_bases`, `documents`, `doc_chunks`, `conversations`, `messages` are multi-tenant with `user_id`.

## RLS

- RLS must be enabled on all user-owned tables.
- Policies must enforce `auth.uid() = user_id` for select/insert/update/delete.

